snippet.title: Making a cursed Horror Game...
snippet.description:
Hello there! This is a Devlog about my first game: Three minutes with your dog. If you enjoyed it and want to follow my journey to new video games, consider subscribing and hitting the like button!

Play the Game: https://capybaraforge.itch.io/three-minutes-with-your-dog

That being said, I hope you have a wonderful day!

Some art was created by Leonardo.AI 🖌️
Gameplay at 0:02 is from the game Phasmophobia.
